sonarr_episodefile_episodeoverviews: Lina and the gang split in two diffent groups, Xellos, Amelia and Zelgadis in one, while Lina, Gourry and Filia in another.  They need to explore two different cities at the same time that seems to be holding magical vessels.  The two countries, Alto, and Bantone hate each other, and Lina and the group experiences their daily cannon ball fight against each other.
